=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_UGen_ex1 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright noisy sound, with noise characteristics, featuring very_slow attack and impulsive envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally dense.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: very_slow
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: impulsive
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: noisy
  spectral_complexity_mean: dense
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 0.0000
  harmonic_decay_rate: 0.0000
  harmonic_regularity: 0.0000
  pitch_clarity: 0.5821
  inharmonicity: 0.0000
  type: noise
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -18.1755
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: UGen Example 1
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Classes/UGen.html
// Tags: UGen, Classes
// ---
// --- Example 1 ---
{ Blip.ar(Blip.kr(4, 5, 500, 60), 59, 0.1) }.play;
